  "text": "To the best of our knowledge, this is the first paper that specifically looks at how well patches are covered over a large number of program versions. Our prior work on testing software patches [CITATION_1] reported the aggregate patch coverage achieved by regression test suites, but the focus was on evaluating the patch testing technique proposed.",
